A Disney Miss Piggy Collection is to debut at Kate Spade New York outlets this holiday season, while the porcine Muppet appears in a promotional campaign for the fashion brand.The campaign, inspired by &#8220;the spirit of disco&#8221; and putting individuality front and center, puts the spotlight on various accessories, handbags, iPhone cases as well as a sweater and features the new &#8216;give it a twist&#8217; collection with a focus on personalization.Meanwhile the glamorous pig puppet will also star in &#8220;Miss Adventure,&#8221; a branded Kate Spade film set for online release in December.Models Jourdan Dunn and Catherine Baba also feature in the photographic campaign, shot by Emma Summerton. -Relaxnews